      "published": "2026-05-23T15:11:47Z",
      "bullets": [
        "Use GitHub's `--ephemeral` flag to automatically tear down runners after a single job, preventing cross-job state pollution and security leaks.",
        "Deploy Actions Runner Controller (ARC) on Kubernetes to autoscale runners dynamically based on active workflow demand, optimizing resource consumption.",
        "Implement local persistent volume mounts or pre-cached Docker images on runners to drastically reduce pipeline latency and network bandwidth usage."
      ]
    },
